# Name: Readme for l2pconverter.py       
# Author:      Sudheer
# Created:     03/03/2014
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is the readme for the script fontconverter.py which converts 
wx transcription to (broad) phonemic transcription using IPA. The 
script uses language-specific *.map files. 

This tar archive contains the following files-
fontconverter.py: main script
hinwx2ipa.map: mapping from wx characters to IPA symbols
hinipa2wx.map: mapping from IPA symbols to wx characters

